{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-26-reciprocal-cycles","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 26: Ciklusi sestre/braće","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Dio broja ima 1 na svojoj najvišoj poziciji/lancu. Predstavljanje ovih delova u decimalnom sistemu sa lancima od 2 do 10 je prikazano:</p>\n<div style='padding-left: 4em; display: inline-grid; grid-template-rows: auto; row-gap: 7px;'><div><sup>1</sup>/<sub>2</sub> = 0.5</div><div><sup>1</sup>/<sub>3</sub> = 0.(3)</div><div><sup>1</sup>/<sub>4</sub> = 0.25</div><div><sup>1</sup>/<sub>5</sub> = 0.2</div><div><sup>1</sup>/<sub>6</sub> = 0.1(6)</div><div><sup>1</sup>/<sub>7</sub> = 0.(142857)</div><div><sup>1</sup>/<sub>8</sub> = 0.125</div><div><sup>1</sup>/<sub>9</sub> = 0.(1)</div><div><sup>1</sup>/<sub>10</sub> = 0.1</div></div>\n<p>Gde 0.1(6) znači 0.166666... i ima ponavljajući ciklus cifre 1. Izgleda da <sup>1</sup>/<sub>7</sub> ima ponavljajući ciklus cifre 6.</p>\n<p>Pronađi vrednost <code>d</code> &#x3C; <code>n</code> za koju <sup>1</sup>/<sub>d</sub> ima najduži period ponavljanja u svom decimalnom zapisu.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3861000cf542c50fe99","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301908,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-26-reciprocal-cycles"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function reciprocalCycles(n) {\n\n  return n;\n}\n\nreciprocalCycles(1000);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>reciprocalCycles(700)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof reciprocalCycles(700) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>reciprocalCycles(700)</code> inapaswa kurudisha 659.</p>","testString":"assert(reciprocalCycles(700) == 659);"},{"text":"<p><code>reciprocalCycles(800)</code> inapaswa kurudisha 743.</p>","testString":"assert(reciprocalCycles(800) == 743);"},{"text":"<p><code>reciprocalCycles(900)</code> trebalo bi da vrati 887.</p>","testString":"assert(reciprocalCycles(900) == 887);"},{"text":"<p><code>reciprocalCycles(1000)</code> inapaswa kurudisha 983.</p>","testString":"assert(reciprocalCycles(1000) == 983);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-26-reciprocal-cycles","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-27-quadratic-primes","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-25-1000-digit-fibonacci-number","id":"5900f3861000cf542c50fe99","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-26-reciprocal-cycles"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}